{"word":"τηνικαῦτα","slug":"τηνικαῦτα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τηνικαῦτα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>commoner form for <a href='S:τηνίκα'><el>τηνίκα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>at that time, then</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>τ. τοῦ θέρους</el> <i>at this time</i> of summer, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>under these circumstances, in this case</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}